                                                is a partner in the Litigation Group of Shearman & Sterling, with a practice involving a variety of complex commercial litigation for U.S. and foreign clients, including a particular emphasis on securities class actions and matters involving financial institutions, fraud allegations and fiduciary duty issues.
                                            











